# Project identity

- **This workspace is AISaravanna** (package name `aisaravanna`). US-first; English default UI, Spanish via `?lang=es` or the header toggle.
- **Git:** The only remote should be `origin` → `https://github.com/kdshah50/AISarvanna.git`. Do not add or push to `naranjogo3` or other remotes unless the user explicitly asks.
- **Docs / examples:** Copy-pasted URLs or names mentioning “naranjogo” may be legacy examples only; default git and release targets are **AISaravanna** (GitHub folder may still be `AISarvanna`).
- **Deploy / CI:** The Next.js app is intended for **Vercel** (GitHub → Vercel). **Do not add or assume GitLab CI** for this repo unless the user explicitly asks.
- **Database:** Env must point to an **AISaravanna-dedicated Supabase project** — never the Mexico marketplace Supabase URL/keys unless the user explicitly says to share them.
